source.oracleReaderQuery:
select  /*+INDEX(t,SPL_SPL_ACTIVE) */ * from betadata.serviceproviderlocations t
where SPL_NAME  like 'Planet Fitness%'

select  /*+INDEX(t1,SPL_SPL_ACTIVE) */  t1.*
from betadata.serviceproviderlocations t1
join betadata.serviceproviders t2 on t1.sp_id=t2.sp_id 
where corp_id=11500  /*Planet Fitness*/
/*where SPL_NAME  like '%Planet Fitness%'  OR SPL_NAME like 'PF%'  */

source.oracleReaderQuery:
select
b.*, a.cggrp, a.cgcpy, a.cgclb, coalesce(CGGRP,CLUB_ABC_COMPANY_NAME) as organization_name  
from dw.club_vw b
left join DW.ABC400FIL_CGFILF_ABC_VW a
on a.club_number_i=b.club_number_i
where coalesce(CGGRP,CLUB_ABC_COMPANY_NAME)   NOT LIKE 'ABC%'
AND coalesce(CGGRP,CLUB_ABC_COMPANY_NAME)   NOT like '%TEST%'
